title Gemini Configuration Workflow
Blipp->UNIS: get initial configuration
note over Blipp: start probes
note right of Blipp: poll interval passes
Web UI->UNIS: user sets configuration
Blipp->UNIS: poll for configuration
note over Blipp: reload probes as necessary
note right of Blipp: poll interval passes
Blipp->UNIS: poll for configuration
note over Blipp: nothing has changed
note right of Blipp: poll interval passes
Web UI->UNIS: user changes configuration
Blipp->UNIS: poll for configuration
note over Blipp
   see changed config,
   reload probes as necessary
end note
